import React from 'react'
import {Container, View, Input, Icon, Text} from '../../../atoms'


const TextIcon = ({placeholder, left}) => {

    return (
        <Container position="relative" style={{
            left: left
        }}>
            <Icon name="search" position="absolute" left="15px" top="9px" width="1.3em"/>
            <Input placeholder={placeholder} width="300px" padding="5px 30px 5px 45px"/>
            <View className="search-results" justify="space-between" align="center">
                <View>
                    <Text>Results of Trigonometry</Text>
                </View>
                <View>
                    <View className="rounded-counter">
                        <Text>4</Text>
                    </View>
                </View>
            </View>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default TextIcon
